attr.title: Dave Gnukem
attr.desc: Dave Gnukem is a cross-platform 2D scrolling platform shooter inspired by Duke Nukem 1.
attr.desc_md: Dave Gnukem is a cross-platform 2D scrolling platform shooter inspired by Duke Nukem 1. It's an open-source clone with similar gameplay, featuring side-scrolling action, platforming, and shooting elements.
